Title: A Lesson in Bravery
Description:
Can you help teach me to be brave like you?

When we played our prank on the witch we made a bunch of Leafy Tricksters angry.  I think the witch did something to them.

Can you show me how you stand up to them?
ObjectivesText: Defeat 8 Leafy Tricksters south of the Jade Witch Hut.
